name: CJKScavengerHunt
0:
”Alexa, open cjk scavenger hunt”
”Alexa, start cjk scavenger hunt”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: c. j. k. scavenger hunt
des: This skill is designed as one part of a multipart scavenger hunt for the CJK Scavenger Hunt Event 2020. This skill will prompt users for a passphrase which will be solved using clues throughout the CJK Scavenger Hunt Event event. Once users provide the passcode, they will be given the next clue and able to proceed in the event.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
